    "content": "<p><img class=\"wscnph\" src=\"//img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/257897/19/14325/805924/678f4373Fd2f5b7ee/02120a7d8e44db3a.png\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则原文】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台工业品/元器件类目资质标准》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=4266&amp;btype=1\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=4266&amp;btype=1</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台宠物生活类目资质标准》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=882556784357806080\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=882556784357806080</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台农资园艺类目资质标准》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=3707&amp;btype=1\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=3707&amp;btype=1</a> </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台个人/个体开店管理规则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=915118822988582912\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=915118822988582912</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台商品价格管理规则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2436&amp;btype=1\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2436&amp;btype=1</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台经营类目商品阈值明细表》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=880256294462820352\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=880256294462820352</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、《京东开放平台个人/个体商品管理规则》</span></p>\n<p sty