ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2401&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台发货管理规则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2488&amp;btype=1\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2488&amp;btype=1</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台个人/个体交易管理规则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1090224406216708096&amp;btype=12\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1090224406216708096&amp;btype=12</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">13</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台送货上门服务规则》</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1092039123323195392\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1092039123323195392</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">14</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、《京东开放平台商家服务管理规则》</s